  <h1>
   draw_set_valign
  </h1>
  This function is used to align text along the vertical axis and changing the vertical alignment will change the position and direction in which all further text is drawn, with the default value being
  <span>
   fa_top
  </span>
  . The following constants are accepted:
  <table>
   <tbody>
    <tr>
     <th>
      Constant
     </th>
     <th>
      Alignment
     </th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      <span>
       fa_top
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/GML/Reference/Drawing/fa_top.png"/><br/>
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      <span>
       fa_middle
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/GML/Reference/Drawing/fa_middle.png"/><br/>
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      <span>
       fa_bottom
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/GML/Reference/Drawing/fa_bottom.png"/><br/>
     </td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">draw_set_valign(valign);
</code></pre>
  <table>
   <tbody>
    <tr>
     <th>
      Argument
     </th>
     <th>
      Type
     </th>
     <th>
      Description
     </th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      valign
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       <a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Drawing/Text/draw_set_valign.htm">
        Vertical Alignment Constant
       </a>
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      Vertical alignment constant (from the table above).
     </td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">N/A
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">draw_set_halign(fa_center);
draw_set_valign(fa_middle);
draw_text(100, 32, "Score: " + string(score));
</code></pre>
  The above code will draw the score centered around the very center of the text.
 </body>
